data.title: Staff Sgt. McCullough
data.meta_description: Talks to a military reporter about his role in assembling and operating the satellite antenna, his training and experience with this type of work, their communications capabilities and his plans to visit the pyramids during his time in Egypt. Also see "Tech. Sgt. Honea" in this section and "Bright Star Antenna Set Up" in the B-roll section.
